                    <span>I have highlighted and underlined all over this book. I have learned an extensive amount. If you are involved in documentary films, or are just learning, this is a must read.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Love this book!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
